Name: Epsilon Jump Prime
About the game: Epsilon Jump is a retro, Geometry Wars-inspired arcade game for Mobile and PC/Mac/Linux devices. The game is based on a unique warping mechanic where you warp through enemies to destroy them, chaining warps together to get a high score. Gameplay involves a unique jumping mechanic on cooldown timer. When the player clicks (on desktop) or swipes in a direction on a joystick (mobile/desktop), it activates a jump which renders the player invulnerable for a fraction of a second as they are quickly warped in the direction they activated the jump in.
